    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔：美联储可能会在下次会议上降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/powell-says-fed-rate-cut-could-be-on-table-at-next-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，最早可能在 9 月降息。在联邦公开市场委员会决定将联邦基金利率维持在 5.25% 至 5.5% 的区间（自去年 7 月以来一直维持在这一水平）之后，他在新闻发布会上发表了讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/powell-says-fed-rate-cut-could-be-on-table-at-next-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 19:02:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储主席鲍威尔称消费者支出稳健，通胀有所缓解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/powell-says-consumer-spending-is-solid-inflation-eased-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，消费者支出有所放缓，但仍保持稳健。他表示，就业市场更加平衡，政策制定者将维持严格的货币政策立场。利率将维持在去年 7 月以来的最高水平。鲍威尔在最新政策决定公布后在华盛顿发表讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/powell-says-consumer-spending-is-solid-inflation-eased-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 18:59:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿克曼旗下潘兴广场美国分公司在削减规模目标后取消 IPO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/pershing-square-usa-withdraws-ipo-after-slashing-size-goal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于一系列障碍阻碍了备受期待的上市，亿万富翁比尔·阿克曼 (Bill Ackman) 旗下潘兴广场 (Pershing Square) 撤回了美国封闭式基金的首次公开募股 (IPO)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/pershing-square-usa-withdraws-ipo-after-slashing-size-goal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 18:48:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储感觉现在处于“最佳状态”：美国银行的加彭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/fed-feels-it-s-in-a-sweet-spot-right-now-bofa-s-gapen-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行证券美国经济部门主管迈克尔·加彭 (Michael Gapen) 在回应美联储决定将利率维持在 20 多年来最高水平时表示：“这是正确的渐进举措。”加彭在接受彭博电视采访时还表示，9 月份降息的可能性有所增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/fed-feels-it-s-in-a-sweet-spot-right-now-bofa-s-gapen-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 18:42:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚通过分歧决议将利率下调至 10.75%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/colombia-cuts-interest-rate-half-a-percentage-point-to-10-75</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于通胀上升削弱了加快货币宽松的理由，哥伦比亚央行在分歧意见下决定将利率下调半个百分点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/colombia-cuts-interest-rate-half-a-percentage-point-to-10-75</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 18:25:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>餐饮业仍在遭受冲击：Styne</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/restaurant-industry-still-suffering-styne-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Lucques Group 联合创始人兼独立餐厅联盟创始成员 Caroline Styne 表示，餐饮业仍处于困境，因为劳动力成本和食品成本上涨。她在“彭博市场”节目中与 Scarlet Fu 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/restaurant-industry-still-suffering-styne-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 18:21:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储维持利率不变，暗示降息将近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/fed-leaves-rates-unchanged-signals-a-cut-is-closer-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国联邦储备委员会官员将利率维持在二十多年来的最高水平，但暗示在通胀放缓和劳动力市场降温的情况下，他们正朝着降低借贷成本的方向迈进。Mike McKee 报道“美联储决定”。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/fed-leaves-rates-unchanged-signals-a-cut-is-closer-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 18:16:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔为 9 月降息铺平道路，美国国债价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/treasuries-rally-into-fed-meeting-with-a-september-cut-at-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示最早可能在 9 月份降息，交易员已完全消化这一预期，此后美国国债价格上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/treasuries-rally-into-fed-meeting-with-a-september-cut-at-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 14:04:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔暗示 9 月降息 新兴资产涨至每日高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/china-stocks-spur-emerging-market-gauge-as-focus-moves-to-fed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于杰罗姆·鲍威尔暗示美联储可能最早在 9 月份的下次会议上降息，新兴市场股票和货币均升至盘中高点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/china-stocks-spur-emerging-market-gauge-as-focus-moves-to-fed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 11:46:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔助长 9 月降息预期 股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔的鸽派言论延续了由主要科技公司飙升开始的股市上涨势头，推动标准普尔 500 指数创下自 2 月份以来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 22:44:39 GMT</pubDate>
